desc: We specialize in Handmade Natural Macrame Plant Hangers in all sizes from Mini-Hangers for Succulents to Large Extra-Large for Tall Ceilings. We also customize for table-top jute plant hangers including cathedral style ceilings. We take pride in our products. Orders are shipped within 24 hours. Shipped from Michigan.

layout.text: We take pride in our craftmanship. Our products are individually handmade. Boho-Chic Vintage Designs. Sizes from Mini to Extra-wide Jute Plant Hangers.
